long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Enter the retro world of Pixel Car Racing, where classic pixel art meets high-octane racing action! Build, tune, and customize your own collection of pixel cars to race through a variety of tracks and modes. Experience dynamic drag and street racing with realistic car physics, and challenge racers from around the world in multiplayer mode. With endless car customization options, from engines to paint jobs, you can create the ultimate pixel racer. Climb the leaderboards, unlock rare cars, and race to victory in this nostalgic, adrenaline-fueled racing experience!
